title: My own club not showing up, but others are still in it.
body:
I made a club a while ago and the tag doesn't show up nor does it show up under the clubs tab. However, my friend who was also in it still has the tag and when he goes on the club page it still shows me as the owner. 

Any way to fix this?

replies.body: I can try and sync it for you to see if it helps, what's the club name and tag?
The club name is Reignover Baegnover and the tag is RnOvr.
Thanks!  I've tried to sync this.  Relog and let me know if that helped!
Yes it did! Thanks so much :)
